{"id": 57910, "date": "2025-08-05T04:00:00", "date_gmt": "2025-08-05T11:00:00", "guid": {"rendered": "https://estreetshuffle.com/?p=57910"}, "modified": "2026-05-12T13:19:04", "modified_gmt": "2026-05-12T20:19:04", "slug": "kingdom-of-days-august-5-2", "status": "publish", "type": "post", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2025/08/05/kingdom-of-days-august-5-2/", "title": {"rendered": "August 5"}, "content": {"rendered": "<p><strong>1971:\u00a0</strong>Bruce joins an acoustic jam session (along with Steve Van Zandt on acoustic slide guitar, Kevin Kavanaugh on piano, and Vini Lopez on pebble-filled soda cans) at an outdoor folk concert organized by Tinker West.</p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"20200\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1971-08-05/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1971-08-05.png?fit=2079%2C844&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"2079,844\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1971-08-05\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1971-08-05.png?fit=758%2C308&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-20200 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1971-08-05.png?resize=758%2C308&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"308\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1971-08-05.png?w=2079&amp;ssl=1 2079w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1971-08-05.png?resize=300%2C122&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1971-08-05.png?resize=1024%2C416&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1971-08-05.png?resize=768%2C312&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1971-08-05.png?resize=1536%2C624&amp;ssl=1 1536w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1971-08-05.png?resize=2048%2C831&amp;ssl=1 2048w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1976:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and the E Street Band play their fourth of six nights at the Monmouth Arts Center in Red Bank.</p>\n<div id=\"v-P8BHqSd0-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='426' src='https://videopress.com/embed/P8BHqSd0?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<p><strong>1977:\u00a0</strong>Bruce holds a recording session for his fourth album at Atlantic Studios in New York City, where he and the band work on &#8220;The Way,&#8221; &#8220;Talk to Me,&#8221; and &#8220;After Dinner&#8221;&#8211;none of which will make the album.</p>\n<p><strong>1978:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and the boys bring the Darkness Tour to Louisville for a night. Bruce loses his place early on during &#8220;Rosalita (Come Out Tonight)&#8221; and the band vamps until Bruce remembers where he was.</p>\n<div id=\"v-2zQ6Z7Uq-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='426' src='https://videopress.com/embed/2zQ6Z7Uq?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/q8rw9izpMaY?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"28544\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1978-08-05-2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/1978-08-05.png?fit=880%2C1645&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"880,1645\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1978-08-05\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/1978-08-05.png?fit=548%2C1024&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-28544 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/1978-08-05.png?resize=758%2C1417&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"1417\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/1978-08-05.png?w=880&amp;ssl=1 880w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/1978-08-05.png?resize=160%2C300&amp;ssl=1 160w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/1978-08-05.png?resize=548%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 548w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/1978-08-05.png?resize=768%2C1436&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/1978-08-05.png?resize=822%2C1536&amp;ssl=1 822w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p>After the show, Bruce sits down for an interview with Australian journalist David White. Listen to the interview below.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/kHJ0u70kAf8?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>1981:\u00a0</strong>Night Two at the Capital Center in Largo on the original River Tour.</p>\n<div id=\"v-pK3XrIXK-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='426' src='https://videopress.com/embed/pK3XrIXK?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<p><strong>1984:</strong> Bruce and the E Street Band kick off a ten-night Born in the U.S.A. Tour stand at the Meadowlands. This show features the tour premiere of &#8220;Jersey Girl&#8221; and is available as part of Bruce&#8217;s official archive series. Watch the pro-shot opening of the show below.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/xQWHgkEPO6M?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/vovP_ZecZQI?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/XE-IIrD8fq8?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/whX8b364K64?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"20165\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1984-08-05a/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1984-08-05a.png?fit=2076%2C1377&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"2076,1377\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1984-08-05a\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1984-08-05a.png?fit=758%2C503&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-20165 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1984-08-05a.png?resize=758%2C503&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"503\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1984-08-05a.png?w=2076&amp;ssl=1 2076w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1984-08-05a.png?resize=300%2C199&amp;